<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><title>$ command line ruby cheat sheets</title><link charset="utf-8" href="/style.css" media="screen" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" /></head><body><div class="main"><div class="header"><h1><a href="/">cheat sheets.</a></h1><code class="header">$ command line ruby cheat sheets</code></div></div><div class="content"><pre>Quick block modifiers:
  Header: hn.
  Blockquote: bq.
  Block code: bc.
  Footnote: fnn.
  Paragraph: p.
  Pre-formatted: pre.
  Numeric list: #
  Bulleted list: *

Quick phrase modifiers:
  _emphasis_
  *strong*
  ??citation??
  -deleted text-
  +inserted text+
  ^superscript^
  ~subscript~
  %span%
  @code@
  
Nested Lists:
  * List A
  ## Item 1
  *** Item 1a

To apply attributes:
  (class)
  (#id)
  {style}
  [language]

To align blocks:
  &lt; right
  &gt; left
  = center
  &lt;&gt; justify

To insert a table:
  |_. a|_. table|_. header|
  |a|table|row|
  |a|table|row|

To insert a link:
  &quot;linktext&quot;:url

To insert an image:
  !imageurl!

To insert a link around an image:
  !mypic.gif!:http://myurl.org/

To define an acronym:
  ABC(Always Be Closing)


Footnote Usage:
  See foo[1].

  fn1. Foo.
  
To reference a footnote:
  [n]
  
Punctuation:
  &quot;quotes&quot; → “quotes”
  'quotes' → ‘quotes’
  it's → it’s
  em -- dash → em — dash
  en - dash → en – dash
  2 x 4 → 2 × 4
  foo(tm) → foo™
  foo(r) → foo®
  foo(c) → foo©

Raw HTML:
  ==no &lt;b&gt;textile&lt;/b&gt;==

  notextile. no &lt;b&gt;textilehere&lt;/b&gt;
  
Extended Blocks:
  bq.. quote
  
  
  continued quote
  
  
  p. paragraph</pre></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="footer">Powered by <a href="http://www.sinatrarb.com/">Sinatra</a>,
